						               													<description>The City of Gears holds many secrets.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One of the more persistent rumors is that a band of outcast engineers lives deep within the rusted bowels of the city.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;No one knows if these mysterious souls exist to help or cause injury...or if they are nothing more than SHADOWS IN THE STEAM...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This CITY OF GEARS expansion pack adds a thrilling new card mechanic to the gameplay. The expansion comes with 35 cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Now, when a a player rolls the Production Dice at the start of his turn and end up with blank results, he may draw one &amp;quot;Shadows in the Steam&amp;quot; card. This cards have different effects that might benefit the player or hinder his opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A player may hold up to three cards in his hand and only one card can be drawn at a time, regardless of how many blank faces the player has rolled.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
